        "action": "Add sign language and lip reading to the national curriculum",
        "additional_details": "This change would also mean other students would be better able to communicate with children with hearing-related disabilities.",
        "background": "I want all schools to be required to teach sign language and lip reading, so young people who are deaf or have hearing-related disabilities have the chance to learn the language they need to move forward with their life in school.",
